  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Estimated blood loss is an important parameter recognized as a standard practice in
      anesthesiology and others medical specialties, with relevant clinical and research
      applications. Currently is no model capable of accurately estimate blood loss. The purpose of
      this study is to evaluate the accuracy of a novel model.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
